---
import { getAllLinks, getCategories } from "../lib/data";
import { SHEET_URLS } from "../lib/constants";

let links = [];
let categories = [];
let error = null;

try {
  links = await getAllLinks();
  categories = await getCategories();
} catch (e) {
  error = e;
}
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Debug Data - alditpra</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #e91e63;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #9c27b0;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    th, td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    th {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .badge-success {
      background: #4caf50;
      color: white;
    }
    .badge-inactive {
      background: #9e9e9e;
      color: white;
    }
    .error {
      background: #ffebee;
      color: #c62828;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      border-left: 4px solid #c62828;
    }
    .sheet-url {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      word-break: break-all;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }
    pre {
      background: #263238;
      color: #aed581;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    .back-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>üîç Debug Data Spreadsheet</h1>
    <p style="color: #666;">Halaman ini menampilkan data yang berhasil dimuat dari Google Sheets</p>

    {error && (
      <div class="error">
        <strong>‚ùå Error:</strong> {error.message}
      </div>
    )}

    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">{links.length}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Total Links Aktif</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);">
        <div class="stat-number">{categories.length}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Total Categories Aktif</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>üìã Sheet URLs</h2>
    <div>
      <strong>Links Sheet:</strong>
      <div class="sheet-url">{SHEET_URLS.links}</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Categories Sheet:</strong>
      <div class="sheet-url">{SHEET_URLS.categories}</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Level 1 Items Sheet:</strong>
      <div class="sheet-url">{SHEET_URLS.level1}</div>
    </div>

    <h2>üìä Categories (active = 1)</h2>
    {categories.length === 0 ? (
      <p style="color: #999;">Tidak ada kategori yang aktif (pastikan kolom 'active' bernilai 1)</p>
    ) : (
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>ID</th>
            <th>Title</th>
            <th>Description</th>
            <th>Icon</th>
            <th>Order</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {categories.map(cat => (
            <tr>
              <td><code>{cat.id}</code></td>
              <td><strong>{cat.title}</strong></td>
              <td>{cat.description || '-'}</td>
              <td>{cat.icon || '-'}</td>
              <td>{cat.order}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    )}

    <h2>üîó Links (active = 1)</h2>
    {links.length === 0 ? (
      <p style="color: #999;">Tidak ada link yang aktif (pastikan kolom 'active' bernilai 1, dan kolom 'id' serta 'name' tidak kosong)</p>
    ) : (
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>ID</th>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Category</th>
            <th>Icon</th>
            <th>Level</th>
            <th>Order</th>
            <th>Link</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {links.map(link => (
            <tr>
              <td><code>{link.id}</code></td>
              <td><strong>{link.name}</strong></td>
              <td>{link.category}</td>
              <td>{link.icon || '-'}</td>
              <td>{link.level}</td>
              <td>{link.order}</td>
              <td style="max-width: 200px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;">
                {link.link || '-'}
              </td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    )}

    <h2>üí° Tips Debugging</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Data tidak muncul?</strong> Pastikan kolom <code>active</code> bernilai <strong>1</strong> (angka, bukan text)</li>
      <li><strong>Link/Category null?</strong> Pastikan kolom <code>id</code> dan <code>name</code>/<code>title</code> tidak kosong</li>
      <li><strong>Header tidak match?</strong> Nama kolom harus lowercase dan persis sama (e.g., "active" bukan "Active")</li>
      <li><strong>Sheet tidak terbaca?</strong> Pastikan spreadsheet sudah di-publish "Anyone with the link can view"</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="/" class="back-btn">‚Üê Kembali ke Home</a>

    <details style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; color: #666;">üîß Raw Data (JSON)</summary>
      <pre>{JSON.stringify({ categories, links }, null, 2)}</pre>
    </details>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
